BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Fearless Gala 2026
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261008T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261008T220000
DTSTAMP:20260719T153609Z
UID:occ-1713@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:Actor's Express marks 39 years with cabaret performances\, sil
 ent and live auctions\, and a tribute to Bruce Cohen.\n\nActor's Express c
 elebrates its 39th year with a benefit built around cabaret performances f
 rom Atlanta theatre performers. The evening includes both a silent and a l
 ive auction\, with food and drink from Endive Catering. Bruce Cohen is hon
 ored for his service and support across Atlanta theatre.
GEO:33.7817253;-84.4160629
LAST-MODIFIED:20260719T153547Z
LOCATION:King Plow Arts Center\, 887 W Marietta St NW\, Suite J-107
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://purchase.actors-express.com/EventAvailability?EventId=37401
END:VEVENT
